data.description:
Don't miss out on this very unique 3 bedroom home sitting on nearly 2 acres with a detached 1-car garage, shed and a detached 6 car
pole barn already equipped with a lift, furnace and water hook-up!!! 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths on the first floor along with first floor
laundry hook-ups and a full apartment upstairs equipped with another kitchen, full bath and a 24 x 13 Living room. 2 entrances to the
upstairs unit so you can rent it out, use it as an oversized mancave or just keep it in the family!!! You have a full basement with a wet
bar and enough room to entertain all of your friends and family!! Outside the back door is a very nice 20 x 18 deck that is fenced in to
protect the animals and kiddos!! The 6-car pole barn is where it's at!!! Plenty of space to store your boat, RV, classic cars, etc.... And it
can be enjoyed year round with it's own heat source!!! All appliances and TV's stay so all you have to do is move in!!!
